                <h3 class="subheading">Interior and Comfort: The M-Lounge Experience</h3>
                <p>Step inside the MG Majestor and the visual transformation is immediate. The cabin, finished in Smoked Ebony interiors with Premium Leather accents, feels like a luxury lounge rather than a car interior. MG has christened this space the M-Lounge, and it is an apt name — everything about the cabin is designed to make occupants feel pampered, relaxed, and at ease. </p>
                <h5 class="subheading">Seating Configuration</h5>
                <p>The Majestor is available in two seating configurations. Buyers can opt for the 6-Seater layout with individual Captain Seats in the second row for a more premium, business-class feel, or choose the more practical 7-Seater layout with a bench seat in the second row. The third row features 60:40 split and flat-fold functionality, allowing the cargo area to be expanded when needed. All second-row seats slide and recline, adding to the versatility of the cabin. </p>
                <h5 class="subheading">Massage and Ventilated Seats</h5>
                <p>The top-spec Savvy variant treats the driver and co-driver to an 8-Mode Massage Seat function, ensuring that even after a long journey, occupants feel refreshed rather than fatigued. The Ventiluxe ventilated seats for the front row add another layer of comfort, particularly useful during the hot Indian summers. </p>
                <h5 class="subheading">Galaxy View Panoramic Roof</h5>
                <p>The Galaxy View Roof is one of the most talked-about features of the Majestor's interior. The large panoramic glass roof opens the cabin up to the sky, transforming the M-Lounge into an open-air experience. Whether gazing at city lights at night or soaking in mountain vistas on a road trip, the Galaxy View Roof adds an element of drama and openness to every journey. </p>
                <h5 class="subheading">JBL Studio 12 Sound System</h5>
                <p>Audio lovers will find much to celebrate in the Majestor. The JBL Studio 12 Sound System features a 12-speaker surround sound layout that delivers rich, concert-hall quality acoustics throughout the cabin. From the front row to the third row, every passenger is enveloped in high-fidelity audio that transforms even a daily commute into an enjoyable experience. </p>
                <h5 class="subheading">64-Colour Ambient Lighting</h5>
                <p>
                    The Majestor features a 64-Colour Ambient Lighting system that allows occupants to set the mood for any journey. Whether a calm, cool blue for a relaxed night drive or a warm amber for a festive family road trip, the lighting system adds a layer of personalisation that elevates the entire cabin experience.
                    <h5 class="subheading">3-Zone Automatic Climate Control</h5>
                <p>Comfort extends to climate control as well. The Majestor comes equipped with a 3-Zone Auto AC system, meaning the driver, front passenger, and rear passengers can each set their preferred temperature independently. The PM 2.5 filter ensures that the air inside the cabin remains clean and healthy, while roof-mounted vents in the second and third rows ensure everyone stays cool. </p>
                <h5 class="subheading">220V Power Outlet and Dual Wireless Charging</h5>
                <p>In a thoughtful practical touch, the Savvy variant includes a 220V Power Outlet (150W) in the second row, allowing occupants to charge laptops, cameras, and other devices on the go. Combined with the Dual Wireless Charger up front and multiple USB ports (1 Type-C and 3 Type-A), the Majestor ensures that connectivity is never compromised on long journeys. </p>
                <h5 class="subheading">12-Way Power Driver Seat with Memory Function</h5>
                <p>The driver's seat is a 12-Way Power Adjustable unit with 4-Way Lumbar Support. The Savvy variant adds a Driver Seat Memory Function, allowing two preset seat positions to be saved and recalled at the push of a button. This is particularly useful for households where the car is shared between drivers of different sizes. </p>
                <h5 class="subheading">Double Decker Storage and Cabin Convenience</h5>
                <p>MG has clearly thought about the practical side of cabin storage as well. The Majestor features a Double Decker Storage console, multiple cup holders and bottle holders, a sunglass holder, illuminated scuff plates, and a roomy front console armrest with a storage box. The Powered Tailgate, which can also be operated with a hands-free kick gesture, makes loading and unloading the boot effortless. </p>
                <p>BikeCarHub Insight: The MG Majestor's interior is genuinely competitive with far more expensive European three-row SUVs when it comes to features per rupee. The combination of massage seats, JBL audio, panoramic roof, and 220V outlet in a single vehicle is extraordinary value.</p>
