                <h3 class="subheading">Advanced Technology: Intelligent Domination</h3>
                <p>The technology package in the MG Majestor is one of the most comprehensive in the segment. From the moment the driver approaches the car, the technology integration is seamless and intuitive. </p>
                <h5 class="subheading">i-SMART 2.0 — 75+ Connected Car Features</h5>
                <p>The Majestor runs on MG's second-generation i-SMART 2.0 connected car platform, which offers over 75 connected car features. The system supports wireless Android Auto and Apple CarPlay, the JioSaavn online music app, Digital Bluetooth Key with a Key Sharing function, Live Location Sharing and Tracking, Anti-Theft Immobilisation, Remote AC control via the i-SMART app, and much more.
                <p>The advanced UI supports widget customisation with multiple homepages, 7-colour widget palette options, and a customisable lock screen wallpaper. Voice command support covers multiple Indian languages including Hindi, English, Tamil, Telugu, Marathi, and Gujarati, allowing hands-free control of AC, audio, navigation, and more. </p>
                <h5 class="subheading">31.24 cm Dual-Screen Setup</h5>
                <p>
                    The front cabin houses two 31.24 cm screens — a full HD Touchscreen Infotainment System and a Full Digital Instrument Cluster side by side. The infotainment screen displays everything from navigation and media to climate control and vehicle settings, while the digital cluster gives the driver all the essential driving information in a clear, modern interface.
                    <h5 class="subheading">Column Gear Shifter and Multi-Function Steering Wheel</h5>
                <p>In a design choice that frees up console space significantly, the Majestor uses a Column-Mounted Gear Shifter rather than a traditional floor-mounted unit. The Multi-Function Steering Wheel keeps all infotainment and driving controls within easy reach, ensuring the driver never needs to take their hands off the wheel for routine adjustments. </p>
                <h5 class="subheading">360 HD Camera and Advanced Parking Aids</h5>
                <p>Parking and maneuvering a vehicle of the Majestor's size is made significantly easier by the 360 HD Around View Camera system, which stitches together feeds from multiple cameras to provide a bird's-eye view of the vehicle and its surroundings. Front and rear parking sensors complement this system for added confidence in tight spaces. </p>
                <h3 class="subheading">Safety: Protecting Every Journey</h3>
                <p>MG has built the Majestor with a robust safety architecture, combining passive safety hardware with advanced active safety technology. </p>
                <h5 class="subheading">6 Airbags and Passive Safety</h5>
                <p>The Majestor features 6 airbags as standard, including Dual Front Airbags, Dual Front Side Airbags, and Dual Full-Length Curtain Airbags that extend all the way to the third row. This ensures protection for all passengers, not just those in the front seats. </p>
                <h5 class="subheading">ADAS Level 2 — Savvy Variant</h5>
                <p>The top Savvy variant adds a comprehensive ADAS Level 2 suite that includes Adaptive Cruise Control (ACC), Automatic Emergency Braking (AEB), Lane Keep Assist (LKA), Lane Departure Warning and Prevention, Forward Collision Warning (FCW), Blind Spot Detection (BSD), Rear Cross Traffic Alert (RCTA), Door Open Warning (DOW), Intelligent Headlamp Control (IHC), and Speed Assist System (SAS). </p>
                <h5 class="subheading">Hill Control Trio</h5>
                <p>The Majestor's safety systems extend to challenging terrain as well. Hill Hold Control (HHC) prevents rollback on inclines, Hill Descent Control (HDC) manages speed automatically on steep downhill sections, and Roll Movement Intervention (RMI) provides stability during aggressive cornering maneuvers. </p>
                <h5 class="subheading">ABS, EBD, ESP, and TCS</h5>
                <p>The standard safety suite includes ABS with EBD and Brake Assist, Electronic Stability Programme (ESP), Traction Control System (TCS), Electronic Parking Brake with Auto Hold, ISOFIX child seat anchors, and speed-sensing auto door locks — ensuring comprehensive protection in everyday driving scenarios. </p>
