                <h3 class="subheading">Price, Pre-Reserve, and Delivery Timeline</h3>
                <p>The official price announcement for the MG Majestor is scheduled for April 2026, and it is expected to shake up the full-size SUV segment significantly. While the exact price is not yet confirmed, the feature list and positioning of the Majestor suggest it will be a compelling value proposition against both domestic and international rivals in the segment. </p>
